#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:150
msgid ""
"Fine-tune highlighting, snippet truncation, and the timing of search "
"requests."
msgstr ""
"Finjustera markering, avkortning av utdrag och tidpunkten för "
"sökförfrågningar."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:156
msgid "Highlight context tokens"
msgstr "Visa kontext runt träffar"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:170
msgid ""
"Number of tokens (words) to include before and after each highlighted match "
"in search result snippets. Higher values show more context around matches."
msgstr ""
"Antal ord (tokens) som ska inkluderas före och efter varje markerad träff i "
"sökresultatens utdrag. Högre värden visar mer sammanhang runt träffarna."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:177
msgid "Snippet truncator"
msgstr "Snippet-trunkerare"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:188
