msgstr "Hakparenteser (t.ex. […])"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:189
msgid "Ellipsis (e.g. … )"
msgstr "Ellips (t.ex. …)"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:190
msgid "None (no truncation marker)"
msgstr "Ingen markör"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:191
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Egen"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:203
msgid ""
"Select any of the predefined markers, or choose 'Custom' to enter your own."
msgstr ""
"Välj en av de fördefinierade markörerna eller välj ”Egen” för att ange en "
"egen markör."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:209
msgid "Debounce search"
msgstr "Fördröjd sökning"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:223
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:278
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:297
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:317
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/quick-search.php:42
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/settings.php:84
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/settings.php:138
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/settings.php:169
msgid "On"
msgstr "På"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:224
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:278
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:297
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:317
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/quick-search.php:43
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/settings.php:85
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/settings.php:139
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/settings.php:170
msgid "Off"
msgstr "Av"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:228
msgid ""
"When enabled, search results are fetched only after the user pauses typing "
"(debounced). When disabled, results appear immediately on every keystroke."
msgstr ""
"När aktiverat hämtas sökresultat först när användaren slutar skriva "
"(fördröjt). När inaktiverat visas resultat omedelbart vid varje "
"tangenttryckning."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:235
msgid "Debounce delay (ms)"
msgstr "Fördröjningstid (ms)"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:249
msgid ""
"How long to wait after the user stops typing before firing the search "
"request."
msgstr ""
"Hur länge man ska vänta efter att användaren slutar skriva innan sökningen "
"utförs."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:259
#: views/admin/settings-tabs/statistics.php:89
msgid "Search statistics"
msgstr "Sökstatistik"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:260
msgid ""
"Record completed searches in WordPress to identify content gaps and popular "
"search terms. Each normalised term is stored only once per anonymous browser "
"session."
msgstr ""
"Registrera slutförda sökningar i WordPress för att identifiera "
"innehållsluckor och populära söktermer. Varje normaliserad term lagras bara "
"en gång per anonym webbläsarsession."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:265
msgid "Enable search logging"
msgstr "Aktivera sökloggning"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:284
msgid "Dashboard widgets"
msgstr "Adminpanelwidgetar"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:299
msgid ""
"Register Latest searches, Failed searches, and Popular searches widgets on "
"the WordPress dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Registrera widgetarna Senaste sökningar, Misslyckade sökningar och Populära "
"sökningar på WordPress adminpanel."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:304
msgid "Require statistics consent"
msgstr "Kräv samtycke för statistik"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:319
msgid ""
"When enabled, no search term or session storage is created until your "
"consent platform explicitly grants statistics consent."
msgstr ""
"När detta är aktiverat skapas ingen sökterm eller sessionslagring förrän din "
"samtyckesplattform uttryckligen godkänner statistik."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:324
msgid "Connect your consent platform"
msgstr "Anslut din samtyckesplattform"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:325
msgid ""
"Run this on every page containing a search field when Pressidium Cookie "
"Consent, Cookiebot, or another consent platform grants or withdraws "
"statistics consent. Run it before search logging is allowed to start."
msgstr ""
"Kör detta på varje sida som innehåller ett sökfält när Pressidium Cookie "
"Consent, Cookiebot eller en annan samtyckesplattform godkänner eller "
"återkallar samtycke för statistik. Kör det innan sökloggningen får starta."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:335
msgid ""
"Replace the final example with the boolean consent value from your platform. "
"The plugin treats consent as denied until it receives true. When false is "
"sent, pending logging stops and the plugin removes its session storage."
msgstr ""
"Ersätt det sista exemplet med det booleska samtyckesvärdet från din "
"plattform. Tillägget behandlar samtycke som nekat tills det tar emot true. "
"När false skickas stoppas väntande loggning och tillägget tar bort sin "
"sessionslagring."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:339
msgid "Search registration delay (seconds)"
msgstr "Fördröjning innan sökning registreras (sekunder)"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:342
msgid ""
"How long a completed query must remain unchanged before it is recorded. This "
"is independent of the search-result debounce setting."
msgstr ""
"Hur länge en slutförd sökning måste vara oförändrad innan den registreras. "
"Detta är oberoende av inställningen för fördröjd sökning."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:347
msgid "Minimum search-term characters"
msgstr "Minsta antal tecken i sökterm"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:350
msgid ""
"Shorter queries are searched normally but are not included in statistics."
msgstr "Kortare sökningar hanteras normalt men ingår inte i statistiken."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:355
msgid "Statistics retention (days)"
msgstr "Lagringstid för statistik (dagar)"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:358
msgid ""
"Search terms and anonymous session hashes older than this are permanently "
"deleted."
msgstr ""
"Söktermer och anonyma sessionshashar som är äldre än detta raderas permanent."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:363
msgid "Automatic cleanup"
msgstr "Automatisk rensning"

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:364
msgid ""
"A daily WordPress cron event removes expired statistics. Ensure WP-Cron runs "
"reliably, or call the command below from your server cron."
msgstr ""
"En daglig WordPress-cronhändelse tar bort utgången statistik. Säkerställ att "
"WP-Cron körs tillförlitligt eller anropa kommandot nedan från serverns cron."

#: views/admin/settings-tabs/advanced-settings.php:366
msgid ""
"Alternatively, run the scheduled event with “wp cron event run "
"typesense_search_prune_statistics”. The command uses the retention period "
"set above."
msgstr ""
"Du kan också köra den schemalagda händelsen med “wp cron event run "
"typesense_search_prune_statistics”. Kommandot använder lagringstiden ovan."

